{"tid":1679402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★零售業生意暴跌恐現攬炒　邵家輝促加強支援","createTime":"2019-10-28T07:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T10:19:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fb32dacf826d5c752da1ede084566845e3735597","tid":1679402,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"批發及零售界議員邵家輝表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">部分零售行業生意跌幅高達70%至80%</span>，坦言持續逾4個月的示威已令業界開始出現「攬炒」情況，要求政府加大擔保額及提供電費、煤氣費等雜費補貼。亦有議員建議政府派發消費券，刺激本土消費。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華回應指，本月訪港旅客數字較去年同期減少一半，預料今年下半年和明年初經濟情況較差，政府已推出90%信貸擔保計劃支援初創微企，但要做到百分百擔保有困難，希望業界理解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191028/bkn-20191028092715906-1028_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191028%2Fbkn-20191028092715906-1028_00822_001.html&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD54hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=5fa8df35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191028/bkn-20191028092715906-1028_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ae998ebc2d799ea56b2ab691050618c907465cc4","tid":1679402,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a17732d92b84cd996ea0f95c7edd33648a107f","tid":1679402,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:48:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2734475381bec3a74e65b4a531218196b69c3689","tid":1679402,"uid":7369,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,